strings: <voice_0x010011AE><se_def>*: stray!
<voice_0x010011AF><se_def>*: I don't know who you are, but I won't let you hurt Master Domenico!
<voice_0x010011B0><se_low>country house: David, who are you hiding from? How to protect yourself, ill health!
<voice_0x010011B1><se_low>country house: hurry
<voice_0x010011B2><se_def>daffodil: This is!
<voice_0x010011B3><se_low>country house: .. Good day Madam! I was thinking about Dominik, you came to get me.
<voice_0x010011B4><se_low>country house: I'm sorry you knew this would happen. This time we are expecting you!
<voice_0x010011B5><se_low>country house: You taught me the magic to defeat an extremist like you!
<voice_0x010011B6><se_low>country house: from you! Get back where you came from! ......beans!
<voice_0x010011B7><se_high>Accuracy: Of course not haha!
<voice_0x010011B8><se_high>Accuracy: Sorry, but wand strength doesn't show how useless your weak magic is.
<voice_0x010011B9><se_high>Accuracy: Four heirs were pronounced dead.
<voice_0x010011BA><se_low>country house: .... Where are you!
<voice_0x010011BB><se_low>country house: No more turtles, nobody can resist my spell!
<voice_0x010011BC><se_high>Accuracy: Time to do it! It's a shame that you did it in vain...
<voice_0x010011BD><se_high>Accuracy: ..what is it? what matter
<voice_0x010011BE><se_high>Accuracy: You are faster than you think.
<voice_0x010011BF><se_high>Accuracy: Hi there. It looks like the tide has finally turned in her favor. If she hadn't bought time, she would have been dead long ago.
<voice_0x010011C0><se_high>Accuracy: Don't worry, it's safe now... you don't want to drink it all at once. I still don't have it
<voice_0x010011C1><se_high>Accuracy: If it were me, I would prepare a proper defense in preparation for the next attack. You can even play!
<voice_0x010011C2><se_low>country house: HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA
<voice_0x010011C3><se_def>daffodil: Many thanks to Dominic! Have you suffered?
<voice_0x010011C4><se_low>country house: This nail will disappear! Now is not the time to screw up my good books.
<voice_0x010011C5><se_def>daffodil: I don't mean... just...
<voice_0x010011C6><se_low>country house: That was enough! Get up, Leopold! Not sure what else you could do?
<voice_0x010011C7><se_def>daffodil: This is!
<voice_0x010011C8><se_low>country house: A University Degree. She owes me something. Faster!
